msg: WICKET-3782 Notifications before and after DOM node replacement
Add Wicket.Event.(subscribe|publish) methods. Now interested parties can registers subscribers and listen on topics.
The topic can be fully qualified (like '/dom/node/added') or wildcard ('*') which will listen for all notifications.
